snippet.title: Last Labyrinth-Lucidity Lost- Xbox version Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Xbox version of Last Labyrinth - Lucidity Lost - is now available!
Last Labyrinth -Lucidity Lost-, playable without a VR headset, was released on May 15, 2023, on Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One. Enjoy the astonishing world of "Last Labyrinth" as it is on a flat-screen monitor. 

VR Escape-the-Room Adventure Game Last Labyrinth is Amata’s first VR Game, which was released on various VR platforms in November 2019, garnering various awards and attention thanks to excellent gameplay. 

Last Labyrinth - Lucidity Lost - Xbox Version Game Overview
Title: Last Labyrinth - Lucidity Lost -
